{
  "stem": "14251.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that helped with the problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, we had been through all kinds of stuff.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't live.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't die.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother was sitting one, I guess, early afternoon in her room, which was our room in that big, big place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a woman who used to come often and bring socks for the soldiers that she had, socks that she had mended, knitted, whatever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was a really, really sweet person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm trying to think of what her name was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Could have been Frau Mischke.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she had a face kind of like Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Elisabeth Abegg.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, some people already radiate a kind of goodness.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can't explain it to you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it's true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She asked what the problem was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in the dark there, my mother said, well, I have this friend, and her daughter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And here's the problem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they need to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They need to find a place to stay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess she may have told them that the friend was a-- were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the woman said, it's really you, isn't it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, my mother didn't know if she was about to be murdered or if she had found help.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The woman said, I'll take care of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so on another little train ride, another hour with one of those little slow trains that are out in the country, we had to go to a place called Gamsau, and that was a sharecropper woman who looked twice as old as she really was.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Husband was at the front.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had a mob of children from small to adult and married.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A daughter-in-law was staying there with her two, two children.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
